<plot>Doctors in three North American cities give us a glimpse into the lives of their refugee patients. The stories told here by the doctors - and by the refugees themselves - shed new light on the immigrant experience. These are stories of resilience in the face of great obstacles such as war, persecution and long, harrowing journeys.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?256674</url></doc>
